Our legal team provides advice and counsel to facilitate the firmâ€™s investments, governance, and other objectives. Whether by assisting our investment professionals in negotiating investments, forming and marketing a fund or representing the firm in litigation, the legal professionals at Blackstone play an integral role in advancing the firmâ€™s business and its relationships with clients, unitholders and regulators.Â  
