such portion released by the Trustee(s), as directed by the
Partnership; provided , that in no way shall the general
release of any Trust Income cause an L/C Partner to be permitted to
reduce the amount of an L/C by any amount.

(vi) (A) Any in-kind
distributions by the Partnership relating to Carried Interest shall
be made in accordance herewith as though such distributions
consisted of cash. The Partnership may direct the Trustee(s) to
dispose of any in-kind distributions held in the Trust Account at
any time. The net proceeds therefrom shall be treated as though
initially contributed to the Trust Account.

